## 🌐 Public Routes

| Method | Route | Controller | Inertia Page |
|---|---|---|---|
- | GET | `/` | `PublicController@home` | `Public/Home` |
- | GET | `/businesses` | `BusinessController@index` | `Public/Directory` |
- | GET | `/businesses/{slug}` | `BusinessController@show` | `Public/BusinessProfile` |
- | GET | `/categories/{slug}` | `CategoryController@show` | `Public/CategoryPage` |
- | GET | `/search` | `SearchController@index` | `Public/SearchResults` |
- | GET | `/pricing` | `PricingController@index` | `Public/Pricing` |
- | GET | `/about` | `StaticController@about` | `Public/About` |
- | GET | `/contact` | `StaticController@contact` | `Public/Contact` |
- | POST | `/contact` | `StaticController@contactSubmit` | — redirect back |
- | POST | `/businesses/{slug}/contact` | `BusinessController@contact` | — redirect back |
- | GET | `/blog` | `BlogController@index` | `Public/Blog/Index` |
- | GET | `/blog/{slug}` | `BlogController@show` | `Public/Blog/Show` |

